          "limitationsAndWarnings": "Not a real cybersecurity tool: This chatbot provides educational insights only and should not be used for real-world security decisions.\nSimplified explanations: Responses are tailored for students and may not include all technical details used in professional cybersecurity.\nAutomation Limitations: While Automated Incident Response is powerful, it is not foolproof—students should consider false positives, automation errors, and human oversight when discussing its use.",
